26.47	Violet_Beauregarde	List of characters in Charlie and the Chocolate Factory	In the novels and films, Willy Wonka is the eccentric owner of a chocolate factory - a factory that workers are never seen to enter, but that truckloads of chocolate and candy exit. Without explanation Wonka holds a contest, hiding five golden tickets within the wrappers of candy bars. The individuals lucky enough to find them are promised both a prize and a private tour of his mysterious chocolate factory.	
